{
  "stem": "21437.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were finishing uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it wasn't-- German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember that it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This had to be done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- Oh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like they wore.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sort of like greenish or brownish something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were various colors because the Wehrmacht sometimes wore a different-- they wore different hats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wore a different-- Obersturmbannfuhrer would have-- which was the highest, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had to-- we-- we were-- it was made.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were just-- we were finishing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's not that the work was really-- that it was very hard, but you had to do it, again, with precision.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you had to total.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know the Germans, everything had to be perfect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you couldn't just get away with missing a stitch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything was hand, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From what we did, the finishing was hand-finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From what I did, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't operate a machine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the time it reached me, it was, you know, hand-finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- I was the last person that would know how to sew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I still had to do it perfect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was from early in the morning till late at night, so I really didn't see, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- at that stage, I didn't know that-- that maybe subconsciously, I still looked for inspiration.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because that was the time, really, that I-- that i had a few books at my disposal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, so I really could read something at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, that was a time where, somehow, my parents made sure that it was available.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was not aware, though, that-- that the inspiration-- at that stage, that the inspiration and that spiritual part.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
